This paper involves techniques for applying artistic styles to images and videos, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The use of neural networks and optimization methods also suggests a potential fit for the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the incorporation of user input for semantic annotation may also relate to the graphics (cs.GR) category.
